<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>tiān hái méi yǒu liàng yé sū yǐ 迦南1107</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 tiān hái méi yǒu liàng yé sū yǐ jǐng xǐng, zhǐ shēn dào kuàng yě qí dǎo fù shén tīng.
 kuàng yě jìng wú shēng chuī lái nán běi fēng, yé sū xīn huǒ rè kuàng yě zǒu líng chéng.
 kàn cāng máng dà de kàn yún yún zhòng shēng, zhǔ de xīn zài tòng zhǔ de xīn shéi dǒng.
 rén dōu zhuān gù yǐ yáng liú lí shān lǐng, shén de jiā zāo nán mù rén chén shuì zhōng.
 tiān hái méi yǒu liàng yé sū yǐ jǐng xǐng, zhǐ shēn dào kuàng yě qí dǎo fù shén tīng.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1107</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>